title: Lazy Jack and the Leprechaun feat. A.J. Buckley, Euan Morton
dc:creator: WBUR
description: A.J. Buckley (SEAL Team) and Euan Morton (Hamilton) headline this Irish tale about a lazy fellow who wants to get rich quick, and the conniving leprechaun who has a big trick up his tiny sleeve.
